        "content": "рџ”Ќ SMART FILTERING\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nOnly processes emails that haven't been verified yet\nвЂў Checks if \"Email Verified\" column is empty\nвЂў Prevents duplicate API calls\nвЂў Saves processing time and API credits\nвЂў Ensures efficient workflow execution\n"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
