        "content": "вљ™пёЏ BATCH PROCESSING\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nProcesses emails one by one to:\nвЂў Respect API rate limits\nвЂў Handle errors gracefully  \nвЂў Ensure reliable verification\nвЂў Track progress per item\nвЂў Maintain data consistency\n"
      },
